<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" ?>
<?xml-stylesheet href="xsl/page.xsl" type="text/xsl" ?>

<page section="release-3.6.3">
  <heading>Release 3.6.3</heading>

  <content>
    <para>
      <release-info version="3.6.3" />
      The 3.6.3 release introduces minor bug fixes and improvements.
    </para>

    <table class="release-notes">
      <tr>
        <td class="head">
          Dependencies bugfix updates.
        </td>

        <td>
          <p>
            HPPC updated to version 0.4.3. Attribute binder updated
            to version 1.1.0.
          </p>
        </td>
      </tr>

      <tr>
        <td class="head">
          Pass-through mode for input clusters
        </td>

        <td>
          <p>
            Added pass-through clustering algorithm and
            accepting input clusters in XML input component.
          </p>
        </td>
      </tr>
      
      <tr>
        <td class="head">
          Workbench tweaks.
        </td>

        <td>
          <p>
            Added configurable snippet length in the Workbench.
            Added "reload and flush caches" button and shortcut.
          </p>
        </td>
      </tr>

      <tr>
        <td class="head">
          Solr component tweaks.
        </td>

        <td>
          <p>
            Added custom XSLT stylesheets for Solr output adapter.
          </p>
        </td>
      </tr>

    </table>

    <hr />

    <p>
      For a complete list of improvements and bug fixes, see <a
      href="http://issues.carrot2.org/secure/IssueNavigator.jspa?reset=true&amp;jqlQuery=project+%3D+CARROT+AND+fixVersion+%3D+%223.6.3%22+ORDER+BY+priority+DESC">JIRA
      issues fixed</a> in version 3.6.3. 
    </p>
  </content>
</page>

